Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:12.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed \Na pirate alliance with Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:41.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their plan was to destroy the \NSMILE manufacturing factory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand rescue a samurai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but after Zoro's sword was stolen,\Nthey got separated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:54.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that the \Nprize for a fighting event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:57.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Corrida Colosseum \Nwas the Flare-Flare Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he decided to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:01.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other competitors, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,were the heavy hitters \Nfrom all over the world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a weight limit for gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do,\Nthere is no chance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will win the Flare-Flare Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That beautiful power belongs only to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Pirate Noble!\NCavendish!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Cavendish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:48.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CAVENDISH OF THE WHITE HORSE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have to tell you my name because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:53.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE CAPTAIN OF THE BEAUTIFUL PIRATES\NBOUNTY: 280 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:53.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...everybody knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Pirate Noble" of the \Nwhite horse - Cavendish-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't expect to see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sinful it is to be this beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect as this rose. That is what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been blessed with \Neverything all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've made it this far without
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eating a Devil Fruit or even really trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just with my natural gifts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you earlier! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! I look awesome this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everybody's half-naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what makes them so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gladiators are just part of a show for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People get excited seeing a loser's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Colosseum, people \Nreally show their true color.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're bottling up frustration, \Nfear, and anger everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hiding their bestiality \Ndeep inside of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they want to let it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants to see a prolonged match\Nbetween heavily armored competitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For them, this competition is just a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take off this cape, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching you take \Ndown that big guy earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Lu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it's Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't confuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Straw Hat Luffy was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the real one is \Nan eight-meter-tall giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat Luffy, I would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed you here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered the New World three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world was talking \Nabout this beautiful rookie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwho was worth over 200 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newspapers covered me everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls went nuts over my wanted posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole all of the \Nposters throughout a town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody was going crazy about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, big star!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who? Me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cavendish-{\i1}sama{\i0}, look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't worry! I'm always looking at you all!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard's War of the Best\Ndrew their attention away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy came into the public spotlight\Nalong with Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,new rookies kept coming up one after another
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became popular as the Worst Generation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wreaked havoc like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporters don't pay attention to me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm gonna kill them!\NThose annoying newcomers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're saying is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To recapture everybody's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would kill as many newcomers as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do so, I'm gonna win the \NFlare-Flare Fruit today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weight is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't ignore me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm gonna win the \NFlare-Flare Fruit at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a competitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look strong but you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, she's not very friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up looking like this old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rebecca. A gladiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:29.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,REBECCA\NA GLADIATOR OF THE CORRIDA COLOSSEUM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.14,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for what you did earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man was a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend? This old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the strongest \Ngladiator in the history
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Corrida Colosseum, named Kyros.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won 3000 out of 3000 matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only wound he ever \Ngot was a single slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He was that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to fight here until 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one in this country knows about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of elders or gladiators in this country\Nhas ever seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the strangest statue in Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know if Kyros the \NGladiator actually existed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nor somebody made up the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when and why they built this statue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is\Nwhat's written on this plate right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although nobody knows about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody wants to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... It's so mysterious but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I like this statue! It's so manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, great warrior - Rebecca-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An undefeated girl!\NWe know you'll do it today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you were happy earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see Spartan who bullied you for \Na long time got his ass kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, idiot! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's looking forward\Nto see you get beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pay attention to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight for the last time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win the Flare-Flare Fruit and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kill Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Mingo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What block are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. I'm in D.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we both survive the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy Store!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's overwhelmingly strong!\NThe man with a paper bag mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Store!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if anyone can defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there is an extraordinary \Nguy in Block A!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he can't get away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy Store!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of Block A is the masked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Store!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got the new hero in the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is he going to take his mask off?!\NFor real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! We all know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an interesting beginning!\NAnd an unexpected competitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle royal of Block \NA - the winner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of Block A is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the captain of the first ship of\Nthe fearful Emperor Blackbeard's group -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The champion I met that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Fighting Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blackbeard Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is such a guy fighting here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it was Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he was so formidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting! Go, Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burgess! Burgess! Burgess! Burgess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blackbeard Pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting\NLuffy will win this thing pretty easily
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe it's gonna be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope no one finds out who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we talk a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a guy who doesn't \Nknow where the factory is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the hell out of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsome high-ranked guy in the Doflamingo Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...and make him cough up where it is...\N--Whoa-whoa! Wait! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking, peeking... Peeking, peeking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go some place else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou shouldn't say such a radical thing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medical team! Give aid to \Nthe injured of Block A.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pirate Mercenary" Hajrudin! Cavendish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And "The Missionary" Gambia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, you don't have to rush like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, there are a bunch of bad eggs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gonna be big trouble if one of \Nthese guys wins the Flare-Flare Fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised about Burgess, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll talk to Issho-san right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, are you talking to yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking to somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:07.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A STAFF OFFICER OF A PIRATE GROUP\N - THE BARTO CLUB - BOUNTY: 67 MILLION BERRIES
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nout there, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.49,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"THE MISSIONARY" GAMBIA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that note?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were whispering those cool guys' names!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Missionary" Gambia. That's... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're a Navy soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, sir? Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything's fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna put your nose in any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(I won't!)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Missionary" Gambia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! Th-That beast is gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to yourself! It's over!\NYou're okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colosseum is still excited\Nfrom the battle of Block A!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how it's going to be for Block B!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many familiar \Nnames, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, here is your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need, maybe, three Navy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:50.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the meantime, let's head for... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:53.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,AN ADMIRAL OF THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Green Bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:58.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,FUJITORA (ISSHO)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need as many medics as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, we have casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to know how many spectators\Nthere are in the Colosseum
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the population of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Instead of the enemy numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIs it necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we have to consider first is\Nnot the number of enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the number of people we have to protect -\Ndon't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Navy soldiers in Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're gonna head for Green Bit now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meet us in front of the Colosseum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Under command of the Admiral,\Nwe put our plan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...into action!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Maynard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for hanging up earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and earlier, I mentioned a name -\N"The Missionary" Gambia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:09.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...who works under Bartolomeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:10.73,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,No. 0429 - CAPMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:10.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can cross it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't him that I saw after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn! That Navy soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:25.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A VICE ADMIRAL OF THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS\N"MAYNARD THE PURSUER"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:24.14,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep going on with the plan here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The medical room is that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough stretchers.\NWalk by yourself if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got beaten badly by the champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:22:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you disguise yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI can't help recognizing the face of the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who put a blot on my record!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
